{"id": "1263284786445684778", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1079677800023347250", "author_name": "juzi6912", "author_bot": false, "content": "原來是這樣！如果有時間的話我去讀一下，補一下奧爾拉頭上的紙張美術資源的設定❤️", "timestamp": "2024-07-18T00:02:43.785000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-07-18T00:04:20.888000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1263346903333081148", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "之前一直盯着小人看，发现打怪身上的攻击特效也是字组成的。顺便，都扫了一圈好像没有遗漏，有漏的就下次再补.jpghttps://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1221527962495484015/1262575489122570290\n\n【狂想诗篇】（怒）攻击特效\n\nélégie au passé\n过去的挽歌\n\nirate\n暴怒的;极其愤怒的", "timestamp": "2024-07-18T04:09:33.605000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-07-18T04:09:54.218000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1263346903001862307", "filename": "Image_1721274885708.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 221868, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1263346903001862307/Image_1721274885708.png?ex=69cc9a7d&is=69cb48fd&hm=66e9087e6417a16a403c699497160b983c14c4ea422b3fb7d73a012c22104a84&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
{"id": "1263365790460280842", "channel_id": "1221527962495484015", "type": 0, "author_id": "1168864875943055370", "author_name": "silverstream_s", "author_bot": false, "content": "这次活动命轮上也稀有的出现了文字，依旧是法语。\n【往昔的花与诗】\n被玫瑰戳穿的纸上写的，就是活动和pv里奥尔拉写的那首，因为篇幅和融蚀原因只放了前四行，并且还没有放完整，也就是（括号里的是纸上看不见的原文）：\nPrends ma main，vous （dites）\nLors（que nos doights se touchent，）\ntu me donnes un （jardin）\nDans notre petit （royaume）\n「握住我的手吧」，你说\n当手指相碰的时候，\n你将赠我一座花园\n在我们渺小的王国里", "timestamp": "2024-07-18T05:24:36.647000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1263365790196043866", "filename": "Image_1721279853823.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1087566, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1221527962495484015/1263365790196043866/Image_1721279853823.png?ex=69ccac14&is=69cb5a94&hm=2cfa3406101cedb84c2db40240877666fbf591553b0d40d094af8224a042b7eb&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1221527962495484015", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "游戏美术资源上的文字", "forum_channel_id": "1181146739198140487"}
